      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPER STRIDE (1) has a terrific record this trip with three wins and one placing from four starts. Scored by half a length last time (25.43) in a Grade 5 over 450m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. MIGHTY HENRY (7) comes here off a placing in quick time (22.46) over 400m at this track. Smart time latest and looks a key chance on that form. PITMAN RINGO (2) had been in super honest form hitting the frame three times on end before finishing sixth (23.00) at Gosford last time. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up this time. POWER ROLEX (3) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a nose second (22.73) in a Grade 5 at this track.",
